    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>TOTAL 3-YEAR COST</strong></td>
      <td><strong>RM1,130</strong></td>
      <td><strong>RM4,050</strong></td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p><strong>Digital locks save RM2,920 over 3 years</strong> while providing superior guest experience.</p>

<h2>Which System is Right for Your Property?</h2>

<h3>Digital Locks Are Best For:</h3>

<ul>
<li><strong>Singaporean Guests:</strong> 70% prefer self check-in</li>
<li><strong>Weekend Properties:</strong> Different guests every week</li>
<li><strong>Late Arrivals:</strong> Guests arriving after 8 PM</li>
<li><strong>Remote Owners:</strong> Owners living outside Melaka</li>
<li><strong>Multiple Units:</strong> Managing more than one property</li>
</ul>

<h3>Physical Keys Work For:</h3>

<ul>
<li><strong>Elderly Guests:</strong> Less tech-savvy demographic</li>
<li><strong>Long-Term Guests:</strong> Monthly rentals (fewer turnovers)</li>
<li><strong>Gated Communities:</strong> Guard house handover available</li>
<li><strong>Budget Properties:</strong> Lower nightly rates (RM150-200)</li>
<li><strong>Hosted Stays:</strong> Owner on-site for greeting</li>
</ul>

