<p><strong>For Singaporean-heavy properties:</strong> Digital locks are non-negotiable. 85% prefer self check-in, and you'll lose bookings without it.</p>

<p><strong>For domestic-focused properties:</strong> Physical keys are acceptable, but we recommend adding a keybox for flexibility.</p>

<p><strong>For mixed markets:</strong> Digital lock with backup physical key option. Best of both worlds.</p>

